{'text': 'Nothing to be good to talk abt.
Temple management must look into how to prioritise your bookings n be responsible when it comes to events.

When u collect payment
You should take responsibility to make sure we get wat we pay for
3rd floor changing room
We went up to get ready
N kids who attend classes are openi our room doors n tel us that d room is theirs
Raja Rani room

We book deco
Plle can be so irresponsible to say over see n did not display our kurhu vilakku n kudam for the parusam preparations

Really very shame to have booked this place n let the groom side put us down

I feel bad becoz initially I was d reason they booked that temple
Or else they would have jus gone to siva krishnan temple or where ever they liked', 'languageCode': 'en'}
